_sText:
mg justsurvive 1_v16

Huge map with many traps from my imagination.

How to respawn?
On server you need bots\players, join spectate and join team again for respawn (if respawnplace is already opened (first one)).
After respawn you can choose teleport to whatever part of the map you want try to beat (if opened).

Play multiplayer with noblock plugin, maybe removebodies too.

With 15 total checkpoints you can choose what you like. You must finish the last trap with your teammates if you want to be in the final partyplace.

64 slots
